<entry id="basta" guid="0c10753e-da10-515d-a852-5985fe655a1f"><lexical-unit><form lang="tl"><text>basta</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="basta_0" guid="176ed90e-07b3-537f-9cf5-032b2268d528"><grammatical-info value="Interjection"/><gloss lang="en"><text>used to react when one refuses to give an explanation: just because!; none of your business!; no need to ask!; whatever!</text></gloss></sense><sense id="basta_1" guid="dbdd3b7d-890c-5cf3-9430-52273617d02a"><grammatical-info value="Interjection"/><gloss lang="en"><text>used to react to one's sudden loss for words during an explanation</text></gloss></sense><sense id="basta_2" guid="fbc66589-8443-54bc-a287-c50c01846478"><grammatical-info value="Interjection"/><gloss lang="en"><text>as long as; provided that; only if</text></gloss></sense><sense id="basta_3" guid="0e278dd0-b7b0-515b-b89e-e4caddf8df42"><grammatical-info value="Interjection"/><gloss lang="en"><text>used to emphasize that one's knowledge or concern is limited: just; all I know is that; all that matters is that; all I can say is that</text></gloss></sense><sense id="basta_4" guid="23548c66-0c7b-5aa6-bd7f-7e4ca411a8a2"><grammatical-info value="Interjection"/><gloss lang="en"><text>just; only; merely (used in the negative)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="basta_5" guid="2006efb1-e57a-5c56-99df-4221a7a887a5"><grammatical-info value="Interjection"/><gloss lang="en"><text>used to emphasize lack of discernment in one's actions: just</text></gloss></sense><sense id="basta_6" guid="9ec5066a-374f-54e2-87f7-de31bd93f232"><grammatical-info value="Interjection"/><gloss lang="en"><text>packaging; packing; baling</text></gloss></sense></entry>
