<entry id="sana" guid="c5129ff9-f135-5f6c-999c-592b36bfad84"><lexical-unit><form lang="tl"><text>sana</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="sana_0" guid="4c943f0f-1658-57d8-994a-78f84cc9eb0f"><grammatical-info value="Particle"/><gloss lang="en"><text>used to express hope or wish in something unknown: hopefully; I wish that</text></gloss></sense><sense id="sana_1" guid="01fba45a-cbc9-5c6b-a5cc-cb7b5b1c962d"><grammatical-info value="Particle"/><gloss lang="en"><text>used to express an unrealized intention or situation</text></gloss></sense><sense id="sana_2" guid="1a6a13fd-3643-58be-8f7d-1ac59005b394"><grammatical-info value="Particle"/><gloss lang="en"><text>used to express disappointment in a desired but unrealized result, especially due to an unfulfilled condition</text></gloss></sense><sense id="sana_3" guid="abcdf0bb-ff5e-567d-b912-a3a434709e56"><grammatical-info value="Particle"/><gloss lang="en"><text>devastated; completely destroyed</text></gloss></sense><sense id="sana_4" guid="aceafcb6-5704-53ed-99d2-d77e5a1cb0b1"><grammatical-info value="Particle"/><gloss lang="en"><text>devastation; complete destruction; ruination</text></gloss></sense><sense id="sana_5" guid="6e6bdf39-3112-5800-9a94-1fe483b31892"><grammatical-info value="Particle"/><gloss lang="en"><text>an aromatic variety of taro</text></gloss></sense></entry>
