<entry id="tumira" guid="27ea0ad9-91ab-502e-bc18-40b2a7f287cb"><lexical-unit><form lang="tl"><text>tumira</text></form></lexical-unit><trait name="morph-type" value="stem"/><sense id="tumira_0" guid="68460ccd-cb42-593e-af8a-59234e65c5f4"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to hit or strike a target one is aiming at (with a bullet, rock, arrow, etc.)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tumira_1" guid="9ca6e102-3a1d-579d-94b2-b66e42f69584"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to take one's turn (of a player in a game, sport, etc.)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tumira_2" guid="ebdd9818-7af1-52c8-875a-a9a117f58f57"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to consume drugs</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tumira_3" guid="5d8cc388-f529-5d56-9477-72b066b75e02"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to have sex; to fuck</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tumira_4" guid="d1d8842a-17aa-5249-b429-99fcfc6f0658"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to say one's piece; to say what one wants</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tumira_5" guid="9fdb0d2b-6506-5ecd-b2de-d0447a91344d"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>complete aspect of tumira</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tumira_6" guid="6ceebe1e-170e-5d82-ac6d-2a6c65161e90"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to live; to stay; to dwell (in a certain place)</text></gloss></sense><sense id="tumira_7" guid="7abfc7d5-5c59-58f1-b1a5-79469590039f"><grammatical-info value="Verb"/><gloss lang="en"><text>to remain; to stay (of water in a low place)</text></gloss></sense></entry>
